<div class="content-page">
  <h1>About Me</h1>
  <p>
    Bremmer Artistry is a ceramic studio creating handmade pottery -- functional pieces like
    teapots, cups, and bowls, alongside more artistic forms. The work centers on ongoing
    experimentation with shape, surface, and firing, often drawing on dynamic natural patterns
    like lightning and rivers.
  </p>

